    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n\r\n<br/> 1. Upload an image or screenshot of your site map, **or** paste your written outline.\r\n\r\n<br/> 2. Prompt AI to generate the **HTML for your full site**, starting with the Home page and including all pages shown in your site map.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Optional Prompt:**\r\n\r\n> Use my site map to create the HTML for my full website. Start with the Home page and include a navigation bar that links to all sections. Each section should have its own page with simple placeholder text or headings for now.\r\n\r\n<br/> 3. Check that all pages connect and match your site map. If something is missing or unclear, update your prompt and try again.",
